summary: Added `--focus=MAX` argument to code-cleanup command
---

Added `--focus=MAX` argument to code-cleanup command
## Summary
Implemented maximum coverage mode that deploys 11+ specialist agents for the most thorough code review possible.

## Changes Made
- Updated argument-hint to include `--focus=MAX`
- Enhanced help section with all options documented
- Added `--focus=MAX` focus mode with:
  - 6 base agents with ALL enhancements combined
  - 5 additional specialists (postgres-pro, penetration-tester, compliance-auditor, chaos-engineer, accessibility-tester)
  - Parallel deployment instructions
  - Announcement template

## Flag Combinations
| Command | Review | Remediation |
|---------|--------|-------------|
| `--focus=MAX` | 11+ agents | Interactive |
| `--all` | 6 agents | Auto (all findings) |
| `--focus=MAX --all` | 11+ agents | Auto (all findings) |

## Related Files
- ~/.claude/plugins/cache/zircote-claude-marketplace/claude-spec/0.6.1/commands/code-cleanup.md:815-918

